         <div xml:id="yyy8Uu-xd7665"><!-- l10-c35 -->
            <head xml:id="yyy8Uu-xd7665-Hd1e103">Caput 35</head>
            <p xml:id="yyy8Uu-xd7665-d1e106">
               <lb ed="#H" n="59"/>CAPUT XXXV. 
      <lb ed="#H" n="60"/>In quo de exmeixeia.
    </p>
            <p xml:id="yyy8Uu-xd7665-d1e113">
               <lb ed="#H" n="61"/>TÎ iexeia, est virtus mansuetudini cognata, stricti juris quod 
      poe<lb ed="#H" n="62" break="no"/>Lnas peccatis aequat, moderatrix, propter causam probabilem; ut  
      <lb ed="#H" n="63"/>cum propter factum aut officium, vel propter salutem publicam aut 
      <lb ed="#H" n="64"/>privatam eorum qui peccant, aut propter scandalum vitandum, 
      ali<lb ed="#H" n="65" break="no"/>quid remittitur de nostro jure in peccatis puniendis aut persequendi. 
      <lb ed="#H" n="66"/>injuriis. 
    </p>
            <p xml:id="yyy8Uu-xd7665-d1e129">
               <lb ed="#H" n="67"/>
               <pc type="indent"/>Est exercenda: 
      <lb ed="#H" n="68"/>I Quia praecepta nobis est a Deo, Gal. 6. v. 1. Philipp. 4. v. 5. 
      <lb ed="#H" n="69"/>II. Quia maxime decet homines qui ex infirmitate variis lapsibus 
      <lb ed="#H" n="70"/>&amp; ipsi sunt obnoxij. 
    </p>
            <p xml:id="yyy8Uu-xd7665-d1e142">
               <lb ed="#H" n="71"/>
               <pc type="indent"/>III. Quia illa unusquisque nostrum indigere ab aliis potest. 
      <lb ed="#H" n="72"/>Opponitur ei nimia indulgentia &amp; rigor importunus. 
      <lb ed="#H" n="73"/>Nimia indulgentia, est peccatum, quum quis non movetur iis 
      re<lb ed="#H" n="74" break="no"/>bus, quibus oportebat moveri ex officio ad poenam irrogandum 
      de<lb ed="#H" n="75" break="no"/>linquentibus secundum mandatum Dei, sed impunita quaevis 
      promi<lb ed="#H" n="76" break="no"/>scue peccata sinit.  
    </p>
            <p xml:id="yyy8Uu-xd7665-d1e161">
               <lb ed="#H" n="77"/>
               <pc type="indent"/>Rigor importunus, est peccatum cum quis erga delinquentes &amp; 
      <lb ed="#H" n="78"/>lapsos inmodice durus est, censuras &amp; reprehensiones illorum 
      spiri<lb ed="#H" n="79" break="no"/>su mansuetudinis minime temperans 
      <lb ed="#H" n="80"/>Hactenus de virtute affectuum moderatrice: sequitur de 
    </p>
            <p xml:id="yyy8Uu-xd7665-d1e174">
               <lb ed="#H" n="81"/>
               <pc type="indent"/>virtute actionum moderatrices.
    </p>
